{"tid":2366841,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"拜登公布1.9萬億美元 每人再派錢1,400美元","createTime":"2021-01-15T01:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T02:19:22.000Z","uid":5737,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"081787c68ff34f8d1087ba8cc0f796a9ed8b6312","tid":2366841,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T01:15:01.000Z","msg":"拜登公布1.9萬億美元 每人再派錢1,400美元<br />\n<br />\n【信報財經新聞】美國候任總統拜登公布最新紓困方案細節，表示新紓困方案規模為1.9萬億美元，當中包括全民派發1400美元，如果加上去年12月派發的600美元，派錢金額合共為2000美元。<br />\n<br />\n每周聯邦失業救濟金額增至400美元，並將計劃延長至今年9月式。聯邦工資最低金額增加至每小時15美元。<br />\n<br />\n向州政府及地方政府援助合共3500億美元。向K-12等級學校及高等教育機構提供合共1700億美元資助。<br />\n<br />\n此外，為全民新冠病毒檢測服務，提供500億美元資金，並向州政府、少數族裔等提供疫苗援助金共200億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/634627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F634627&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=27a9c0bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/634627</a>"},{"pid":"b86f873fbbd75129d66308ed4db35261ab1e4c66","tid":2366841,"uid":5737,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T01:15:45.000Z","msg":"選拜登 發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9447118ad030f46fd87714966b3c45adfa3373f5","tid":2366841,"uid":364767,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"民主黨不得民心，唯有派錢平息民憤"},{"pid":"4750b048c8c34addec0c03ed7297561774b392ef","tid":2366841,"uid":56148,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T01:17:34.000Z","msg":"侵話派2000 俾人ban 9 左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a3485578c7b789786ab76ba7900f68111d3716","tid":2366841,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T01:19:41.000Z","msg":"做開低下層都未必有呢個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 